<paragraph blockId="45.[189,1399,1368,1500]" pageId="45" pageNumber="46">
Plant ca 
<quantity box="[297,373,1368,1394]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="45" pageNumber="46" unit="cm" value="10.0">10 cm</quantity>
high. Stem: 
<quantity box="[534,640,1368,1394]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="45" pageNumber="46" unit="mm" value="3.0" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="2.0">2–4 mm</quantity>
wide when dry, internodes 
<quantity box="[982,1100,1368,1395]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.75" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="0.5" pageId="45" pageNumber="46" unit="cm" value="1.75" valueMax="3.0" valueMin="0.5">0.5–3 cm</quantity>
long. Stipules: 
<quantity box="[1295,1399,1368,1395]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.0" metricValueMax="7.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="45" pageNumber="46" unit="mm" value="6.0" valueMax="7.0" valueMin="5.0">5–7 mm</quantity>
long. Leaves: petiole 
<quantity box="[451,544,1403,1429]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.5" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="45" pageNumber="46" unit="cm" value="2.5" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="1.0">1–4 cm</quantity>
long, densely pubescent; lamina symmetric, upper surface dark green, underside red, dense red tomentose on veins only; margin shallow wide dentate. Inflorescence: bracts 2–5 × 
<quantity box="[270,341,1473,1500]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="45" pageNumber="46" unit="mm" value="2.0">2 mm</quantity>
. Fruit: capsule 7–9 × 
<quantity box="[598,669,1473,1500]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" pageId="45" pageNumber="46" unit="mm" value="3.0">3 mm</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
