<paragraph blockId="45.[189,1399,1585,1612]" box="[189,1399,1585,1612]" pageId="45" pageNumber="46">
Endemic to the Sillet and Jaintia Hills; 
<quantity box="[638,789,1585,1612]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.0" metricValueMax="11.5" metricValueMin="4.5" pageId="45" pageNumber="46" unit="m" value="800.0" valueMax="1150.0" valueMin="450.0">450–1150 m</quantity>
. Flowering: July to August; fruiting: July to October.
</paragraph>
